## 1. Midjourney

**Website:** https://www.midjourney.com/

### Prompt 1: Hero Image - Stem Separation Concept

```
Professional screenshot of a digital audio workstation interface showing AI stem separation. Dark theme UI with a waveform being split into 4 colored layers: red vocals, blue drums, purple bass, green other instruments. Modern flat design, subtle glow effects, clean typography showing "Stemperator". Technical but approachable aesthetic, 16:9 aspect ratio --ar 16:9 --v 6
```

### Prompt 2: Workflow Visualization

```
Infographic style image showing audio production workflow. Left side: single mixed audio waveform in white. Center: glowing AI processing node with neural network pattern. Right side: 4 separated stem tracks in red, blue, purple, and green. Dark background, modern UI aesthetic, music production software style, clean and professional --ar 16:9 --v 6
```

### Prompt 3: REAPER-style Interface

```
Digital audio workstation interface mockup, dark grey theme similar to REAPER. Timeline showing 5 horizontal tracks with colorful waveforms: original track muted in grey, vocals track in coral red, drums in sky blue, bass in purple, other in mint green. Track names visible on left panel. Photorealistic software screenshot style, 4K resolution --ar 16:9 --v 6
```

