## 3. Ideogram

**Website:** https://ideogram.ai/

Ideogram is bijzonder goed in tekst rendering, ideaal voor UI mockups.

### Prompt 1: Software Dialog Mockup

```
Software interface mockup, dark theme. A dialog window titled "Stemperator - AI Stem Separation" with checkboxes labeled "Vocals", "Drums", "Bass", "Other" each with a colored indicator (red, blue, purple, green). Dropdown menu showing "htdemucs". Two buttons at bottom: "Cancel" and "Separate". Clean modern UI design, slight drop shadow, professional audio software aesthetic. Photorealistic screenshot style.
```

### Prompt 2: Feature Highlight Image

```
Professional software marketing image. Dark background with text "STEMPERATOR" in modern sans-serif font at top. Below, 4 horizontal audio waveforms stacked vertically, each in different color: coral red labeled "VOCALS", cyan blue labeled "DRUMS", purple labeled "BASS", mint green labeled "OTHER". Subtle glow effect on waveforms. Text at bottom: "AI-Powered Stem Separation". Clean, minimal design. 16:9 aspect ratio.
```

### Prompt 3: Workflow Diagram

```
Technical infographic showing audio stem separation process. Left: icon of audio file with musical notes. Center: box labeled "Stemperator AI" with circuit/neural pattern. Right: 4 branching arrows leading to 4 icons - microphone (red), drums (blue), bass guitar (purple), piano keyboard (green). Dark theme, modern flat design, professional music technology aesthetic. Text labels clearly readable. Horizontal layout, 16:9.
```

---

## Tips voor beste resultaten

1. **Genereer meerdere variaties** - Maak 4-8 versies en kies de beste
2. **Upscale** - Gebruik de upscale functie voor hogere resolutie
3. **Edit/Inpaint** - Corrigeer kleine fouten met inpainting tools
4. **Consistentie** - Gebruik dezelfde seed/style voor een coherente set

## Aanbevolen afbeeldingsformaten voor README

| Gebruik | Formaat | Resolutie |
|---------|---------|-----------|
| Hero/banner | 16:9 | 1920x1080 of 1280x720 |
| Inline screenshot | 16:9 | 800x450 |
| Logo/icon | 1:1 | 256x256 of 512x512 |

## Na generatie

Upload de afbeeldingen naar `/home/flark/GIT/Stemperator/docs/images/` en voeg ze toe aan de README met:

```markdown
![Stemperator Hero](docs/images/hero.png)

![Stem Separation Workflow](docs/images/workflow.png)
```
